title: PunEmu 1.1 [CEMU69] wbfs
description:
platform wii

A self-assembled, legal Wii disc containing a total of 5 popular emulators released . The purpose of this disc is playing ROMs burned via disc or USB Loader. After unpacking the archive is created including a 38 MB large WIBF file that you then as a tool in WBFS appropriate partitions and transmitted to the loader can run via USB.

The following emulators are included:

FCE Ultra GX R507 (NES emulator)
Snes 9x GX R625 (SNES emulator)
VBA GX R494 (GBA Emulator)
Genesis Plus GX R501 (Sega Megadrive Emulator)
Wii64 Beta 1.1 (N64 Emulator)

please seed

when loading roms, choose settings and select load from dvd in each game section otherwise you won't see the roms.

Special thanks to the creator of punemu 1.1
